title: She's All Caught Up!.
description: She's All Caught Up! is a cautionary tale for young people enamored by the fast life and for the older folks who love them. This memoir tells of the negative influences that swayed the early life of author Jamila T. Davis (creator of the Voices of Consequences Enrichment Series.) She is currently serving a 151 month federal sentence for her role in a multi-million dollar bank fraud scheme.
author: Jamila T. Davis
